}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Plans
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/plans

### Create Razorpay Order (Replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/create-razorpay-order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "plan": "bronze"
}

### Confirm Payment (Replace TOKEN and TRANSACTION_ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscription/confirm-payment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "plan": "bronze",
  "transactionId": "pay_test123",
  "gateway": "razorpay"
}

